title: ATD 2018 Session | Wanted: More Leadership! Tips and Tools to Unleash Leadership Potential

json.text: Hi! My name is Janice Burns, and I'm the Vice President of Product Management at DDI.
I'm a Senior Consultant in the product management group at DDI.
Tom and I are presenting a session at ATD on Sunday, May 6 titled: Wanted: More Leadership!
Tips and Tools to Unleash Leadership Potential.
We're going to share with you some of our latest research, tools, and diagnostics for
identifying and unleashing potential within your organization.
Guaranteed that you will walk away with tools and insights that you can use right away in
Can't wait to see you there!
